      "content": "wait really? appendicitis? that sounds so dramatic lol. i feel like i just ate something weird or its just the cramps being extra this month. i don't really want to go to the emergency room at 2am if i don't have to, it's so expensive and the wait is insane. if i just take a couple of the codeine and an ibuprofen now, wouldn't that just help me sleep through it so i can see how i feel in the morning? surely a little bit won't hurt?",
