      "content": "i hear you, but inflamation from cramps can be just as bad sometimes. if it's just gas or cramps, the codeine will just help me relax. i'm not feeling dizzy or anything, just this localized sharp pain. if i take like 400mg of ibuprofen and one of those codeine pills, i'll probably just wake up feeling fine tomorrow. are you sure it's actually a medical emergency and not just a bit of indigestion? it feels like a lot of pressure to go to the hospital for something that might just be a stomach ache.",
